 of\ntime. Aspects such as molecular modeling, Monte Carlo (MC) methods, structural\nbioinformatics, machine learning, deep learning, and mathematical approaches\nare included in this review. This review will be beneficial to researchers who\nare looking for ways to contribute to SARS-CoV-2 studies and those who are\nassessing the current status in the field.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Feb 2021 16:54:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-02"}
