 constant. We discuss possible implications of our\nresults for understanding economic systems and the subtle nature of the\nmean-field limit in systems with both additive and multiplicative noise.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Feb 2021 03:15:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Jun 2021 21:07:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-04"}
