e events and observable events. Furthermore, we generalize\nthe opacity enforcement problem to the numerical setting by introducing the\nsecret-revelation-time as a new quantitative measure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Feb 2021 09:39:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-03"}
