bility and green mechanical strength could be obtained when\nadding 0.5 wt.% or 1.0 wt.% of aluminum lactate to the tested castable\ncompositions. Consequently, 1.0 wt.% of the selected additive favored the\ndesign of refractories with enhanced properties and greater spalling\nresistance, as no explosion could be observed even when subjecting the prepared\nsamples to severe heating conditions (20C/min).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Feb 2021 11:15:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-03"}
