 a non-polynomial primary\npseudo-polynomial starting from any primary pseudo-polynomial generated by a\n$G$-function different of $1/(1-x)$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Feb 2021 15:02:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Aug 2021 15:56:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-09"}
